        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "The first to meet him was Sahim, who kissed his feet in the stirrups and said, \"May thy hand never wither, O champion of the age!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
