        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Then they carried him into the city of Oman, where he entered his palace and sat down on the throne of his kingship, whilst his officers stood around him in the utmost joy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
