        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Whoso accepteth the Faith spare him; but if he refuse slay him.\"--And Shahrazad perceived the dawn of day and ceased to say her permitted say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
