        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "CHAPTER five",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "JACK AND THE BEAN STALK'S FARM.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "It was quite an ordinary looking farm yard and quite an ordinary looking Cow, but she stared so earnestly up at Davy that he felt positively certain she had something to say to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "As he sat up, feeling exceedingly foolish, he looked anxiously at the Cow, expecting to see her laughing at his misfortune, but she stood gazing at him with a very serious expression of countenance, solemnly chewing, and slowly swishing her tail from side to side.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "As Davy really didn't know how to begin a conversation with a Cow, he waited for her to speak first, and there was consequently a long pause. Presently the Cow said, in a melancholy, lowing tone of voice, \"The old gray goose is dead.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"I'm very sorry,\" said Davy, not knowing what else to say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"She is,\" said the Cow, positively, \"and we've buried her in the vegetable garden.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Nothing came up but feathers.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"That's very curious,\" said Davy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Curious, but comfortable,\" replied the Cow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "The pig sleeps there, and calls it his quill pen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"So do I,\" said Davy, laughing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"What else is there in the garden?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Nothing but the bean stalk,\" said the Cow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"You've heard of 'Jack and the Bean stalk,' haven't you?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Oh! yes, indeed!\" said Davy, beginning to be very much interested.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"I should like to see the bean stalk.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "By the way, that's the house that Jack built.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000012_000000",
