        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Davy turned and looked up at the house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "It certainly was a very pretty house, built of bright red brick, with little gables, and dormer windows in the roof, and with a trim little porch quite overgrown with climbing roses.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Suddenly an idea struck him, and he exclaimed:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Then you must be the Cow with a crumpled horn!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"It's not crumpled,\" said the Cow, with great dignity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"There's a slight crimp in it, to be sure, but nothing that can properly be called a crump.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Then the story was all wrong about my tossing the dog.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "It was the cat that ate the malt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Certainly not,\" said the Cow, indignantly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Who ever heard of a cow tossing a cat?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Well, you can,\" said the Cow, indifferently.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"She isn't much to see.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "If you'll look in at the kitchen window you'll probably find her performing on the piano and singing a song.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "She's always at it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Davy stole softly to the kitchen window and peeped in, and, as the Cow had said, Mother Hubbard was there, sitting at the piano, and evidently just preparing to sing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "The piano was very remarkable, and Davy could not remember ever having seen one like it before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "The top of it was arranged with shelves, on which stood all the kitchen crockery, and in the under part of it, at one end, was an oven with glass doors, through which he could see several pies baking.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Mother Hubbard was dressed, just as he expected, in a very ornamental flowered gown, with high heeled shoes and buckles, and wore a tall pointed hat over her nightcap.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "She sang in a high key with a very quavering voice, and this was the song:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "While she was singing the song little handfuls of gravel were constantly thrown at her through one of the kitchen windows, and by the time the song was finished her lap was quite full of it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"It's Gobobbles,\" said the Cow, calmly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"You'll find him around at the front of the house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"No,\" said Davy, greatly surprised at the question.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"It's precisely what I should expect of a person who would fall out of a window.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Of course you couldn't,\" said the Cow, yawning indolently.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Boy,\" said Mother Hubbard, beaming mildly upon Davy through her spectacles, \"you shouldn't throw gravel.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"I haven't thrown any,\" said Davy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"I am speaking the truth,\" said Davy, indignantly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"It was Gobobbles.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"It would have been far better if he had been cooked last Christmas instead of being left over.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000043_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000043_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "Stuffing him and then letting him go has made a very proud creature of him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000043_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000043_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "You should never be proud.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"I'm not proud,\" replied Davy, provoked at being mixed up with Gobobbles in this way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Proud means being set up, I think,\" he said, respectfully; \"but I don't think I know any examples.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"You may take Gobobbles for an example,\" replied Mother Hubbard.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000047_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000047_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "He was tied fast in a baby's high chair, and was thumping his chest with his wings in such a violent and ill tempered manner that Davy at once made up his mind not to aggravate him under any circumstances.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000047_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000047_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "As Gobobbles caught sight of him he discontinued his thumping, and, after staring at him for a moment, said sulkily:--",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Why not?\" said Davy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8422/283572/8422_283572_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8422",
        "content": "\"Oh, they're so hungry!\" said Gobobbles, passionately.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8422_283572_000050_000001",
